{"tid":1524270,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵復仇行動","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:08:48.000Z","uid":951,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"59c8727dba8af15b597ef929bffad34d18a7c80a","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"今日黨鐵所作所為大家有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要比所以人知道佢企緊係香港人既對立面！<br />\n我地一定要做返啲野！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一：<br />\n黨鐵廣告係一大收入來源<br />\n你話唔打人唔私了都算<br />\n死物廣告唔係咁都要潔癖呀嘛？<br />\n<br />\n第二：<br />\n呼籲大家齊心協力跳閘！<br />\n齊心協力係要所有人一齊有呢個共識<br />\n同埋好多人唔跳係因為驚比人捉到<br />\n所以我地如果見到有人比人捉<br />\n要即刻上去掩護被捉義士撤離<br />\n同時都唔好on99企定定比人捉比人拎身分證<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跑啦on9！</span></span><br />\n你即刻跑走冇人會捉你架！<br />\n而你即刻跑得走，掩護你既巴絲打亦都可以全身而退<br />\n<br />\n第三：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵總部大樓（英語：MTR Headquarters Building）為香港鐵路有限公司的總部所在，位於香港九龍觀塘區九龍灣偉業街33號德福廣場2期。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"c45b524cbe0baa7b05c5fc42e4362e856b85e550","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"db9a83f02b322d89e7b892d1421d6f56d5b8aad6","tid":1524270,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c633cf99883d9e6af751bb5dbaffa02a19d0e9b0","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"再推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5264f5d578df162ce49292163e697d82f67f3f44","tid":1524270,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試下找不同？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6be131d5145d4dafb3cb8eaba688b0c971c8788e","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"推上熱門！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e900e936423b43e4ad247e305e2e08edd5aed1e5","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"推到多啲人見到！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113d8d5e0f4fd22da92f1202701bd58e2b3be49","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"我要全世界都知！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ea28b1b7a4a2d37399f4ec889391e3cf0062e2","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dda8ca69e5bcf5058022e6ea1e2c91cdd6a67c","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a947c026c0764ab10f00b0187fbe814eb2f4e08c","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"自推100次"},{"pid":"2473a18c20a67e0c2272db1ecf313f002badc00f","tid":1524270,"uid":951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:16.0